    "commitMessage": "Presence: Handle no JSON config loaded at power-on\n\nThis change blocks the system from power-on if no JSON configuration has\nbeen loaded. It prevents an indeterminate state because the presence\nsensing cannot publish any meaningful values if it has no configuration.\n\nSigned-off-by: Mike Capps <mikepcapps@gmail.com>\nChange-Id: I3203b4cc1e845a0e3c62aa67581581513787bcd0\n",
